name: Little Teracotta Dress
description:
Pleated versatile dress, in a rich teracotta colour, suitable for a wide range of events. Get glamorous with the detachable velvet bag, that allows you and your hands to be free at any party! Soft trim with fringes. 
Bag and chain included. 

Available in sizes 38, 40, 42.

Fabric: viscose and wool blend and 100% acetate lining.

name: Subtil Polka
description:
Pleated velvet dress, very feminine, in the 50's spirit. The fabric has a beautiful subtil polka dott print. The length is just under the knees and has side pockets. Perfect for a special event or cocktail! 
 
Available in size 38 and 40.

100% cotton velvet with acetate lining.
